subject: H_a97w8r2xm921u6y
stimulus:
1. You will see a sequence of letters presented one at a time. Your task is to determine if the letter on the screen is the same that appeared on the last screen.
  2. If the letter is a match press the M key.
  3. For example, if you saw the sequence X, C, C, B, B, X you would press the M key when the second C appeared and similarly when the second B appeared on the screen.
  4. You do not need to press any key when there is not a match.

subject: H_a97w8r2xm921u6y
stimulus:
The sequence will begin on the next screen.

This is a practice trial. Lets see how focused you are.

Remember: press the M key if a letter appears on simultaneous screens.
